NAME:
   flight desktop doctor - System health check

USAGE:
   flight desktop doctor [options]

CATEGORY:
   Desktop types

DESCRIPTION:
   Perform a health check on the system to check that all dependencies are present.

OPTIONS:
   --help, -h  show help

GLOBAL OPTIONS:
   --log-level LEVEL  set the log LEVEL (debug, info, warn, error, fatal). Default: warn
